# 🧬 2. Yocto layer

* Создаем кастомный `meta-smartmonitor`

* Включаем пакеты:

  * `gstreamer1.0`, `pulseaudio`, `libc`, `libstdc++`, `rustc + cargo`

* Добавляем systemd сервис:

  ```ini
  [Unit]
  Description=SmartMonitor Service
  After=network.target

  [Service]
  ExecStart=/usr/bin/smart_monitor
  Restart=always

  [Install]
  WantedBy=multi-user.target
  ```

* Yocto recipe (`smartmonitor.bb`):

```bitbake
SUMMARY = "SmartMonitor embedded firmware"
LICENSE = "MIT"
SRC_URI = "git://repo.url;branch=main"
S = "${WORKDIR}/git"

DEPENDS = "gstreamer1.0 pulseaudio rust"
```

